Whether they've visited us
or not, I'm not convinced.

00:11:11.050 --> 00:11:14.180
Most UFO footage
looks like a hoax.

00:11:14.180 --> 00:11:17.140
Whether panspermia was
responsible for putting life

00:11:17.140 --> 00:11:21.690
on Earth, whether the building
blocks of life were sent here.

00:11:21.690 --> 00:11:23.870
That idea of panspermia
is kind of amazing.

00:11:23.870 --> 00:11:26.190
Especially because Freeman
Dyson, the physicist,

00:11:26.190 --> 00:11:27.660
says we need to do that soon.

00:11:27.660 --> 00:11:30.380
We need to take all the
DNA of life on Earth

00:11:30.380 --> 00:11:33.449
and send it out into space.

00:11:33.449 --> 00:11:33.990
So who knows?

00:11:33.990 --> 00:11:37.000
Maybe some intelligent
super alien intelligence

00:11:37.000 --> 00:11:39.390
did that to seed the
life on this planet.

00:11:39.390 --> 00:11:40.890
It's interesting
to speculate about.

00:11:45.170 --> 00:11:47.692
I love the mystery of that,
the possibility of that.

00:11:47.692 --> 00:11:49.150
There's an interesting
thing called

00:11:49.150 --> 00:11:53.066
the transcension hypothesis
that I made a video about that

00:11:53.066 --> 00:11:54.690
tries to explain
Fermi's Paradox, which

00:11:54.690 --> 00:11:56.523
is if the universe is
so vast, why don't see

00:11:56.523 --> 00:11:59.420
any evidence of these
extraterrestrial civilizations?

00:11:59.420 --> 00:12:03.530
And the reason is that as
complexity and technology

00:12:03.530 --> 00:12:05.830
evolves, we stop
expanding outwards,

00:12:05.830 --> 00:12:08.007
and we start expanding inwards.

00:12:08.007 --> 00:12:10.340
The whole thing about STEM
compression-- the compression

00:12:10.340 --> 00:12:11.690
of space, time,
energy, and matter--

00:12:11.690 --> 00:12:14.106
means we start to put more
computation and more complexity

00:12:14.106 --> 00:12:15.490
into denser and denser spaces.

00:12:15.490 --> 00:12:17.290
Until you have
computation at the level

00:12:17.290 --> 00:12:19.640
of the nano scale
and the femto scale.

00:12:19.640 --> 00:12:21.630
And literally, you're
concentrating [INAUDIBLE]

00:12:21.630 --> 00:12:23.254
into a point where
you literally create

00:12:23.254 --> 00:12:26.040
black hole-like conditions,
and virtual realities

00:12:26.040 --> 00:12:28.540
and digital minds disappear
into those black hole-like

00:12:28.540 --> 00:12:30.140
conditions and
slingshot to the end

00:12:30.140 --> 00:12:31.870
of the universe, the
end of space-time.

00:12:31.870 --> 00:12:35.420
And that's where all the other
extraterrestrial civilizations

00:12:35.420 --> 00:12:35.920
are.

00:12:35.920 --> 00:12:37.794
And so that's why we
don't see them anywhere,

00:12:37.794 --> 00:12:40.140
because they exist outside
of the observable universe.

00:12:40.140 --> 00:12:42.440
Because of this inevitable
STEM compression

00:12:42.440 --> 00:12:46.560
that happens when technology
reaches that singularity.

00:12:46.560 --> 00:12:49.750
That's why we can't
see the aliens.

00:12:49.750 --> 00:12:50.250
Maybe.

