Try to explain to
chimp the nuances

00:14:58.742 --> 00:14:59.825
of a Shakespearean sonnet.

00:14:59.825 --> 00:15:00.990
You know what I mean?

00:15:00.990 --> 00:15:01.820
It's not that easy.

00:15:01.820 --> 00:15:03.360
They don't have
the mental software

00:15:03.360 --> 00:15:05.564
to be able to run
that in their heads.

00:15:05.564 --> 00:15:07.480
Which is a shame, because
they're missing out.

