00:15:56.640 --> 00:16:00.030
and emergence-- just like
10 trillion cells decided

00:16:00.030 --> 00:16:02.230
to team up and become
the super-organism called

00:16:02.230 --> 00:16:05.050
the human being, now
billions of human beings

00:16:05.050 --> 00:16:07.410
are teaming up and becoming
this super-organism called

00:16:07.410 --> 00:16:09.620
the internet, and the
internet is wiring all of us

00:16:09.620 --> 00:16:11.520
together like
individual synapses.

00:16:11.520 --> 00:16:14.385
And these synapses are
becoming this global brain.

00:16:14.385 --> 00:16:15.760
And that eventually,
when there's

00:16:15.760 --> 00:16:18.710
sufficient interconnection
and sufficient complexity,

00:16:18.710 --> 00:16:20.660
a new kind of
planetary consciousness

00:16:20.660 --> 00:16:21.935
might emerge from that.

00:16:21.935 --> 00:16:23.690
And it's one of those
things where you can't plan.

00:16:23.690 --> 00:16:24.900
That's the whole
thing about emergence.

00:16:24.900 --> 00:16:27.110
[INAUDIBLE] complexity leads
to something different.

00:16:27.110 --> 00:16:29.990
The sum of the parts adds
up to more than the parts.

00:16:29.990 --> 00:16:31.424
That is what emergence is.

00:16:31.424 --> 00:16:32.882
So even if that
did happen, I don't

00:16:32.882 --> 00:16:34.965
