00:26:42.840 --> 00:26:43.760
I love those guys.

00:26:47.250 --> 00:26:49.810
"What do you think of David
Pearce's idea of utopia?"

00:26:49.810 --> 00:26:51.160
I love David Pearce.

00:26:51.160 --> 00:26:52.120
I love him.

00:26:52.120 --> 00:26:54.407
