I think, is brilliant.

00:26:54.407 --> 00:26:55.740
Everybody should check that out.

00:26:55.740 --> 00:26:58.810
It's this online treatise on
how we should use biotechnology,

00:26:58.810 --> 00:27:02.421
nanotechnology, to engineer
suffering out of existence.

00:27:02.421 --> 00:27:03.420
Like physical suffering.

00:27:03.420 --> 00:27:05.760
Like pain, malaise,
death, disease.

00:27:05.760 --> 00:27:07.300
Literally eliminate it.

00:27:07.300 --> 00:27:10.300
And just literally
transform ourselves.

00:27:10.300 --> 00:27:13.470
Like caterpillars turning
themselves into butterflies.

00:27:13.470 --> 00:27:14.900
It plays out in nature.

00:27:14.900 --> 00:27:16.030
Why can't we do it?

00:27:16.030 --> 00:27:17.010
We are nature, too.

00:27:17.010 --> 00:27:18.510
That's a thing you
shouldn't forget.

00:27:18.510 --> 00:27:20.760
We are nature.

00:27:20.760 --> 00:27:22.200
Everything we do is nature.

